{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775842725131,"sessionID":"ses_2878688b6ffeo9bpkBg84IeBsN","part":{"id":"prt_d78798c7d001MPO6Gmg6ks7Vh0","messageID":"msg_d78797839001FnHwoX1QQWiOGl","sessionID":"ses_2878688b6ffeo9bpkBg84IeBsN","type":"tool","tool":"grep","callID":"toolu_72243b4ae8f543ff92360f73","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"pattern":"AR-005|Sandbox.*Processor|workloadmanager"},"output":"Found 138 matches (showing first 100)\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/pkg/workloadmanager/design.md:\n  Line 1: # AR-005: Sandbox 创建处理器 (Sandbox Creation Processor)\n  Line 3: - **AR ID**: AR-005\n  Line 4: - **Module**: pkg/workloadmanager\n  Line 18: pkg/workloadmanager/\n  Line 226:     wm := workloadmanager.NewWorkloadManager(client)\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/.sdd_prompt.md:\n  Line 3: AR: AR-005 — Sandbox 创建处理器\n  Line 4: Module: pkg/workloadmanager\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-005/delta-spec.md:\n  Line 1: # Delta Spec: AR-005 — Sandbox 创建处理器\n  Line 5: This delta-spec defines acceptance scenarios for implementing the Sandbox creation handler in `pkg/workloadmanager`. The Sandbox creation handler is responsible for provisioning sandboxed execution environments based on AgentRuntime and CodeInterpreter configurations.\n  Line 9: - **AR**: AR-005\n  Line 10: - **Module**: `pkg/workloadmanager`\n  Line 19: ### AR-005-001: Create Sandbox from AgentRuntime\n  Line 28: ### AR-005-002: Create Sandbox from CodeInterpreter\n  Line 38: ### AR-005-003: Sandbox creation with custom parameters\n  Line 46: ### AR-005-004: Sandbox creation validation failure\n  Line 53: ### AR-005-005: Sandbox creation for non-existent resource\n  Line 63: ### AR-005-010: Get Sandbox Status\n  Line 75: ### AR-005-011: List Sandboxes\n  Line 83: ### AR-005-012: Delete Sandbox\