{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775842778421,"sessionID":"ses_2878688b6ffeo9bpkBg84IeBsN","part":{"id":"prt_d7879e189001dPfsKFrBu1zpps","messageID":"msg_d7879c921001udCqPqmpuEjayH","sessionID":"ses_2878688b6ffeo9bpkBg84IeBsN","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_04f450c137324d8e98846ebd","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# AR-005 — Sandbox 创建处理器 Tasks\n\n**Module:** pkg/workloadmanager  \n**Language:** Go  \n**Size:** M  \n**Stage:** ST-3 (Design Completed)\n\n---\n\n## Phase 1: Core Handlers\n\n- [ ] **1.1** Update `pkg/workloadmanager/types.go` - Add `CreateSandboxRequest`, `CreateSandboxResponse`, `SandboxEntryPoint` types with Validate() method\n- [ ] **1.2** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/defaults.go` - Constants: DefaultSandboxTTL, DefaultSandboxIdleTimeout, label/annotation keys (SessionID, WorkloadName, SandboxName, IdleTimeout)\n- [ ] **1.3** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/informers.go` - GVR variables (SandboxGVR, SandboxClaimGVR), Informers struct, Start() and WaitForCacheSync() methods\n- [ ] **1.4** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/sandbox_controller.go` - SandboxReconciler struct, WatchSandboxOnce() returning channel, getSandboxStatus()\n- [ ] **1.5** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/k8s_client.go` - K8sClient struct with dynamic client, informer factory, listers; ClientCache for per-user clients; GetOrCreateUserK8sClient()\n- [ ] **1.6** Update `pkg/workloadmanager/handlers.go` - Add handleAgentRuntimeCreate() handler function\n- [ ] **1.7** Update `pkg/workloadmanager/handlers.go` - Add handleCodeInterpreterCreate() handler function\n- [ ] **1.8** Update `pkg/workloadmanager/server.go` - Register new routes POST /v1/agent-runtime, POST /v1/code-interpreter\n\n---\n\n## Phase 2: Workload Builder\n\n- [ ] **2.1** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/workload_builder.go` - buildSandboxObject() converting AgentRuntime to Sandbox unstructured object\n- [ ] **2.2** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/workload_builder.go` - buildSandboxClaimObject() for WarmPool path\n- [ ] **2.3** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/workload_builder.go` - buildEntryPoints() to construct SandboxEntryPoint array from podIP and TargetPorts\n- [ ] **2.4** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/workload_builder.go` - resolvePodIP() with annotation, lister, and ownerReference fallback logic\n\n---\n\n## Phase 3: Sandbox Creator\n\n- [ ] **3.1** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/sandbox_creator.go` - sandboxCreator struct with k8sClient, sandboxController, storeClient, publicKey fields\n- [ ] **3.2** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/sandbox_creator.go` - createSandbox() method implementing full flow (watcher registration → store placeholder → CR create → wait running → resolve IP → store update)\n- [ ] **3.3** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/sandbox_creator.go` - rollback logic for CR deletion and store cleanup on timeout/failure\n- [ ] **3.4** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/sandbox_creator.go` - Handle WarmPoolSize > 0 path (create SandboxClaim vs Sandbox)\n\n---\n\n## Phase 4: Auth & GC\n\n- [ ] **4.1** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/auth.go` - authMiddleware with token validation, context keys (userToken, serviceAccount, serviceAccountName, namespace)\n- [ ] **4.2** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/auth.go` - validateServiceAccountToken() using TokenReview API\n- [ ] **4.3** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/garbage_collector.go` - garbageCollector struct with store client and k8sClient\n- [ ] **4.4** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/garbage_collector.go` - gcLoop() for periodic cleanup of expired sandboxes\n- [ ] **4.5** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/garbage_collector.go` - cleanupExpiredSandboxes() with 2-minute tick interval\n\n---\n\n## Phase 5: Error Handling\n\n- [ ] **5.1** Implement error types: ErrAgentRuntimeNotFound, ErrCodeInterpreterNotFound, ErrTemplateMissing\n- [ ] **5.2** Map error types to HTTP status codes in handlers (400 for validation, 401 for auth, 404 for not found, 500 for internal)\n- [ ] **5.3** Add error response DTOs in types.go (ErrorResponse with Message field)\n\n---\n\n## Phase 6: Integration Points\n\n- [ ] **6.1** Integrate with client-go: import AgentRuntimeInterface, CodeInterpreterInterface, SharedInformerFactory\n- [ ] **6.2** Integrate with Store: call StoreSandbox(), UpdateSandbox(), DeleteSandboxBySessionID()\n- [ ] **6.3** Integrate with SandboxReconciler: call WatchSandboxOnce() for status waiting\n\n---\n\n## Phase 7: Unit Tests\n\n- [ ] **7.1** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/workload_builder_test.go` - TestBuildSandboxObject_ValidRuntime\n- [ ] **7.2** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/workload_builder_test.go` - TestBuildSandboxClaimObject_WarmPool\n- [ ] **7.3** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/workload_builder_test.go` - TestBuildEntryPoints_DefaultPorts\n- [ ] **7.4** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/workload_builder_test.go` - TestResolvePodIP_FromAnnotation\n- [ ] **7.5** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/workload_builder_test.go` - TestResolvePodIP_FromOwnerReference\n- [ ] **7.6** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/sandbox_creator_test.go` - TestCreateSandbox_Success\n- [ ] **7.7** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/sandbox_creator_test.go` - TestCreateSandbox_Timeout\n- [ ] **7.8** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/sandbox_creator_test.go` - TestCreateSandbox_RollbackOnFailure\n- [ ] **7.9** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/handlers_test.go` - TestHandleAgentRuntimeCreate_Success\n- [ ] **7.10** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/handlers_test.go` - TestHandleAgentRuntimeCreate_MissingPodTemplate\n- [ ] **7.11** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/handlers_test.go` - TestHandleCodeInterpreterCreate_WarmPool\n- [ ] **7.12** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/handlers_test.go` - TestHandleCodeInterpreterCreate_AuthModePicoD\n- [ ] **7.13** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/types_test.go` - TestCreateSandboxRequest_Validate table-driven tests\n- [ ] **7.14** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/auth_test.go` - TestAuthMiddleware_ValidToken\n- [ ] **7.15** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/auth_test.go` - TestAuthMiddleware_MissingToken\n- [ ] **7.16** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/garbage_collector_test.go` - TestGarbageCollector_ExpiredSandbox\n\n---\n\n## Phase 8: Integration Tests\n\n- [ ] **8.1** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/integration_test.go` - E2E test with real K8s cluster (TestE2E_CreateAgentRuntimeSandbox)\n- [ ] **8.2** Test warm pool pre-provisioning with CodeInterpreter WarmPoolSize > 0\n\n---\n\n## Phase 9: Verification\n\n- [ ] **9.1** Run `go build ./pkg/workloadmanager/...` - successful compilation\n- [ ] **9.2** Run `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/...` - all unit tests pass\n- [ ] **9.3** Run `go test -race ./pkg/workloadmanager/...` - no race conditions\n- [ ] **9.4** Run `go vet ./pkg/workloadmanager/...` - no issues\n- [ ] **9.5** Run `golangci-lint run ./pkg/workloadmanager/...` - linter passes\n- [ ] **9.6** Verify test coverage > 40% with `go test -coverprofile=coverage.out ./pkg/workloadmanager/...`\n\n---\n\n## Dependencies\n\n| Task | Depends On |\n|------|------------|\n| Phase 1 | AR-004 (WorkloadManager HTTP 服务框架), client-go library |\n| Phase 2 | Phase 1 (types, defaults, informers) |\n| Phase 3 | Phase 1 + Phase 2 |\n| Phase 4 | Phase 1 (k8s_client) |\n| Phase 5 | Phase 1 (types) |\n| Phase 6 | client-go, store package, SandboxReconciler |\n| Phase 7 | Phase 1-5 (implementation complete) |\n| Phase 8 | Phase 7 (unit tests) |\n| Phase 9 | All phases |\n\n---\n\n## References\n\n- Design: `sandbox-orchestration/AR-005-sandbox-creation-processor/design.md`\n- Delta Spec: `changes/AR-005/delta-spec.md`\n- Related AR: AR-004 (WorkloadManager HTTP 服务框架)","filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-005/tasks.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-005/tasks.md","exists":true,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-005/tasks.md","time":{"star